   <note>2 tifs. Five baseball players practice in the field with the Copper Basin in the background. In the second picture, the empty green football field appears in sharp contrast to the barren landscape behind it. Copper mining in the Ducktown-Copperhill area in Polk County began in the mid-1800s. By the earlier 20th century the area was environmentally devastated.</note>
